title: IT music: Sphenx times three (AWE64 Gold)
description:
A compilation of 3 tracks from Sphenx.

00:00 Abandoned Chip City (v1.01, 2000)
04:04 Crystal Sweet (v4.00, 2007)
07:59 Outer Galaxy Space Rock (v1.18LQ, 2008)

Art:
1. Facet/Genesis Project^Lemon - Light Of Struggle, 2nd at Revision 2022
2. Pikku Myy - Luna 2014, 6th at Gerp 2014
3. Mon/Oxygene - Unknown title, 7th at GASP 1995

- Retro PC circa 2002. MS-DOS 7.1 (Win98SE), Athlon XP 2200+ etc.
- Impulse Tracker 2.14v5 and AWE64 Gold CT4390 (as SB16) analog out
- Maxed out channels (/L256)
- 32-bit interpolation and 45454 mixing rate, filter and feedback disabled
- MIXERSET.EXE treble and bass in neutral position (no fade or boost)
